column5: Hi all,Heading to Murray Lake (up just East of Wawa) in a couple weeks. Wondered if anyone had any fishing reports or other relative info.Thanks!!Walleye65
Can't help you but maybe you can help me. We are heading there on July 25 for 4 days of fishing. Would love a report before we leave. Don
We are heading up next week July 11th. When are you guys going up?
Be up same week. First time on this lake for us....have you fished it before?
No its my first time too. My buddy has been up there before. I hope it's good. I've been going to another lake for about 30 years almost always do well there. I know that lake very well tho.

Kinda hoping for any info. Good or bad I would still like to hear. If I asked for info but didn't care to give any after my trip,that just doesn't seem right(trying to say this as nicely as I can)Don.
sent you a PM on Tuesday.
